    "body": "This drops the dependency on `lspconfig.util`, which appears deprecated.\r\n\r\nThis also makes it possible to use just the config file without the rest of the framework.\r\n\r\nThe root pattern grouping and prioritisation follows the one proposed here: https://github.com/ocaml/ocaml.org/pull/3322/files#diff-6721080d4f565e09348cab4e8fe6d6393b9e4449bf9c7e2b3f054a0b986809d6R224\r\n\r\nTested with NeoVim v0.11.4",
    "closed_at": "2025-09-24T23:29:46Z",
    "comment_data": [
        {
            "_links": {
                "html": {
